    "description": "<strong>Saikyo Robots</strong> combines real time strategy and roguelike. <br>Daytimes are calm. Command your army, grow it, gather resources and explore the wasteland.<br>Upgrade your base and army to create the strongest robot army there is! Why? <br>Because the cloud king won't stop attacking your base, every single night!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379530/extras/c2183b174cfd4e30fb3facc3cd789f86.avif?t=1726156482\" width=608 height=84 /></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379530/extras/453bd84388e435518af8c51f1fb2ce9c.poster.avif?t=1726156482\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379530/extras/453bd84388e435518af8c51f1fb2ce9c.webm?t=1726156482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379530/extras/453bd84388e435518af8c51f1fb2ce9c.mp4?t=1726156482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Robots follow your command to fight, collect, repair and build. Lead your army wisely!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379530/extras/d349a3765028c4c3a207147ab7164f99.avif?t=1726156482\" width=608 height=84 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379530/extras/b53d0fc66e5f176ac24068c5af83c4a6.poster.avif?t=1726156482\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379530/extras/b53d0fc66e5f176ac24068c5af83c4a6.webm?t=1726156482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://sh